Package dkeep.logic

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Map
    Interface defining common methods for Map classes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Club
    Class that extends basic Entity object functionality.
    DrunkenGuard
    Class that extends basic Guard object functionality.
    DungeonMap
    Class implementing Map interface with Dungeon specific behavior.
    Entity
    Class that stores information common to all dynamic game objects.
    Stores coords in Point format and object representation in char format.
    Game
    Class responsible for all game logic and game world data.
    Stores current map and entities and allows manipulation of entities.
    GameSaveHelper
    Class responsible for serializing game data (creates/restores a copy since Game is static)
    Guard
    Class that implements basic Guard object functionality, to be extended by other Guard types.
    Hero
    Class that implements Hero object functionality, considered the Player character.
    KeepMap
    Class implementing Map interface with Keep specific behavior.
    Ogre
    Class that extends basic Entity object functionality.
    RookieGuard
    Class that extends basic Guard object functionality.
    SuspiciousGuard
    Class that extends basic Guard object functionality.
